        "header": "Section 4Modeling",
        "images": [
            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.11289/2606.11289v1/x6.png",
                "caption": "Figure 8:Text encoders’ performanceacross benchmarks. Under our modeling setup, the encoder-decoder T5Gemma models outperform representative decoder-only LLM/VLMs and CLIP-style models. More results in AppendixC.",
                "position": 849
            },
            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.11289/2606.11289v1/x7.png",
                "caption": "Table 3:Concatenating two copies of T5Gemma-2B feature sequencesand using two separate MLP adapters (equivalent to combining two T5Gemma-2B text encoders) yields a similar improvement as combining different text encoders, whereas using a shared MLP adapter does not. This suggests the improvement may come from additional adapter parameters, not separate text encoders.",
                "position": 972
            },
            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.11289/2606.11289v1/x8.png",
                "caption": "Figure 10:Using larger adapters for the text encoder consistently improves performanceacross backbone architectures. Beyond 2 transformer blocks, using larger adapters brings marginal further gains.",
                "position": 1030
            },
            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.11289/2606.11289v1/x9.png",
                "caption": "Figure 11:Long skip connections(bao2023all)can improve the performance-parameter trade-off for dual-stream models. Additional FLOPs-based analysis is in Figure44, and results on other backbone families are in AppendixC.7.",
                "position": 1326
            },
            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.11289/2606.11289v1/x10.png",
                "caption": "Figure 12:Backbone family. We compare cross-attention, single-stream, and dual-stream backbones across model sizes (see Figure41for training FLOPs analysis). We find that the dual-stream backbone achieves the best overall performance.",
                "position": 1355
            }
        ]
